### ─── CATEGORIES ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3. Get all categories
### File: src/GroceryShop.Api/Controllers/CategoriesController.cs
### Flow: CategoriesController.GetAll()
###   → ICategoryService.GetAllCategoriesAsync()
###   → CategoryService (Infrastructure) queries DbContext
###   → EF Core LINQ: .Where(c => c.IsActive).OrderBy(c => c.DisplayOrder)
###   → Returns CategoryDto records with ProductCount
GET http://localhost:8020/api/v1/categories

