### ─── PRODUCTS ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### 5. Get all products (paginated, default page 1, size 20)
### File: src/GroceryShop.Api/Controllers/ProductsController.cs
### Flow: ProductsController.GetAll()
###   → IProductService.GetProductsAsync(page, pageSize, filters...)
###   → ProductService builds LINQ query with dynamic filters
###   → .Where(p => p.IsAvailable) ← soft-deleted products excluded
###   → .Skip((page-1)*pageSize).Take(pageSize)
###   → Returns PagedResult<ProductDto> with TotalCount, HasNextPage
GET http://localhost:8020/api/v1/products?page=1&pageSize=5

###

### 6. Filter: organic products only
GET http://localhost:8020/api/v1/products?isOrganic=true&pageSize=5

