### 32. Chat: custom scenario — order tracking (skips RAG entirely)
### File: ai-service/app/services/custom_responses.py
### Flow: check_custom_scenario("track my order") → { skip_rag: true }
###   → Returns canned response, NO embedding, NO Qdrant, NO LLM
###   → Still persisted to Redis + PostgreSQL
POST http://localhost:8021/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Where is my order? Can you track it?",
    "session_id": null
}

###

### 33. Chat: custom scenario — brand not carried (RAG continues)
### Flow: check_custom_scenario("kirkland") → { skip_rag: false }
###   → Prepends apology, then runs full RAG for alternatives
